Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.40,0:02:20.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}boku tachi wa eien ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.40,0:02:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We will be forever{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:23.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}tooi mukashi sou kimeteita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}decided long ago in the past{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sanji and Pudding's bloodbath wedding\Nfinally began.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.50,0:02:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others executed a mission\Nin which they planned to make Big Mom shriek.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.63,0:02:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Their plan was...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.67,0:02:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...to break her most-treasured portrait of\NMother Carmel, the mysterious nun,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.01,0:02:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and show it to her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.81,0:03:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At last, Big Mom has started shrieking.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Mom's Secret!\NThe Giant's Island Elbaph and a Little Monster!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mother...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please listen to me, Mother...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.26,0:03:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No one listens to what I say.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, Mother... Where did you go?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big Mom's tears...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.36,0:03:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's behind them goes back 63 years ago\Nto Elbaph in the New World.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.31,0:03:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That is where the world-famous Giants,\Nthe Warriors of Elbaph, lived.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.93,0:04:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.10,0:04:21.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,CHARLOTTE LINLIN\N(A HUMAN, FIVE YEARS OLD)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.06,0:04:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the name of this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you about it later.\NCome on down now, Linlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.03,0:04:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.49,0:04:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?\NAre you going to go somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy has work to do near here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.71,0:04:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Linlin, can you be a good girl\Nand wait for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I'm coming with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.05,0:04:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a good girl, you can eat as \Nmany sweets from the bag as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.17,0:04:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:04:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:05:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of them?!\NThen, I'll wait, I'll wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.14,0:05:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.27,0:05:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.83,0:05:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Linlin...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.09,0:05:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After having caused that much damage,\Nwe're lucky she's only being deported.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.62,0:05:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is... more than we can handle...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.38,0:05:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say the Holy Mother lives here.\NShe'll save Linlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.33,0:05:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's set off! This area is dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.35,0:05:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.25,0:05:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Those are big fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.00,0:06:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.73,0:06:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.01,0:06:21.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,GROWL
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.94,0:06:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's snowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they back yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:39.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,GROWL
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.78,0:06:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange.\NThey've been gone for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.83,0:06:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momma, Papa... Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.92,0:06:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you coming back?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:07:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Regarding Elbaph,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}a century ago, it was home to Giant warriors\Nthat were feared by the world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They were the Giant Pirates!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.15,0:07:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They raised havoc on the seas everywhere\Nand burned down countless cities.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.03,0:07:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.38,0:07:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}one day, all of a sudden,\Nthe Giant Pirates lost their two captains{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.47,0:07:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and passed into legend.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.90,0:07:30.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shortly thereafter, several of its stragglers
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.27,0:07:32.32,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,who weren't careful after \Nthe loss of their leaders,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:35.80,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}were caught by the Navy\Nand were about to be executed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.82,0:07:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Halt the execution!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven is asking for reconciliation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.69,0:07:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A beautiful wandering nun appeared!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.28,0:07:59.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,SISTER CARMEL
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.46,0:08:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her name was Sister Carmel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.89,0:08:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven is asking for reconciliation?\NWhat are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.05,0:08:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how much terror\Nthey caused...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.06,0:08:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An even greater reason for penance!\NWhy can't you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.47,0:08:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you kill them,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.57,0:08:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the warriors of Elbaph will form an army\Nto seek revenge against humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.23,0:08:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive their sins!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.11,0:08:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lead them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To a world where all races join hands
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and share laughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:09:02.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They eventually called Carmel "Mother"\Nand opened an orphanage...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.69,0:09:05.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,...{\i1}called "House of Lambs" \N{\i0}{\i1}where she took in children
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.83,0:09:10.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,of any race or birth, who had no place to go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:14.10,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On Elbaph where the Giants live...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.12,0:09:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At the same time, she worked as a bridge\Nbetween the Giants and humans...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.11,0:09:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then, 37 years later...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.24,0:09:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mother Carmel met Linlin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in good hands now, Linlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until your mom and dad come back,\Nlet's be friends and live together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.17,0:09:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They won't come back!\NYou've been abandoned!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.74,0:09:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All children here are very unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So unique that our parents dumped us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.72,0:09:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll become friends with them\Nin no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.39,0:09:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.87,0:09:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.73,0:09:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're huge! Are you a Giant?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat then!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.76,0:10:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There was a prince who got expelled\Nfrom his country in the aftermath of a coup...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.24,0:10:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And a child who was almost enslaved\Nbecause of poverty...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All these troubled children\Nwho couldn't be controlled even by their parents...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...were living in the village of the Giants\Nregardless of their birth or race.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.56,0:10:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.77,0:10:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she new?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}More than anything, to Linlin\Nwho had always been bigger than the others,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.32,0:10:34.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Elbaph was the first place she'd seen
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.02,0:10:38.22,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,where people, houses, and \Neverything else fit her size,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and she was very comfortable.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.30,0:10:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.35,0:11:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not good to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.36,0:11:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! It's not good to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother always says "Be nice to each other"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:39.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE NEXT DAY
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.17,0:11:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did it happen? Why did it happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.44,0:11:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. What's the matter, Linlin?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.14,0:11:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bear and a wolf were \Nfighting in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.30,0:12:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not good to fight and I thought\NI had to help them become friends
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I put them in the same cage yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.62,0:12:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the bear ate the wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I hit the bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.86,0:12:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bear seems sorry.\NHow many times did you hit him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just once...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.50,0:12:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She killed the bear with a single blow?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.22,0:12:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just wanted them to become friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.31,0:12:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Linlin, you're so sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.58,0:12:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let's go play with everyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.25,0:12:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To Linlin, Carmel was the first person ever\Nto really understand her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it! Linlin killed a \Nbear with a single blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.56,0:13:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.22,0:13:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear Eyri-{\i1}kun{\i0}, the Giant,\Ngot injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.23,0:13:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She tried to hit a mosquito on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.59,0:13:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She broke several of his bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.66,0:13:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Linlin?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.89,0:13:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.79,0:13:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's got one too many elbow joints\Nso I thought it'd be nice to tear it apart for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.00,0:13:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he's from the Longarm Tribe!\NThat's normal for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.07,0:13:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Linlin, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got fins so I thought it'd help by\Ntearing them off for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.22,0:13:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that. The Fish-Men often have\Ncharacteristics of fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.89,0:13:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.69,0:13:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was terrified!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.26,0:14:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, forgive her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.03,0:14:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Linlin is a kind girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.73,0:14:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Carmel pardoned everything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.53,0:14:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.20,0:14:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Linlin will kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.93,0:14:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait! Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.45,0:14:22.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,KASHII
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.45,0:14:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}10 months later in Elbaph, the \NNew World's strongest country,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}tough ones had accepted \NLinlin open-heartedly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:31.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,OIMO
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.84,0:14:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.35,0:14:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost been 40 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever seen a duel last that long?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.89,0:14:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, never! Let's go and pick them up\Nafter another decade or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.27,0:14:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}These Giants - Kashii and Oimo -\Nare talking about...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.86,0:14:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dorry the Blue Ogre.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.21,0:15:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Brogy the Red Ogre.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They met Luffy and the others\Nand bonded tightly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.75,0:15:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will not let them\Ndestroy your pride, friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.86,0:15:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have faith in us, and \Ncontinue straight ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.77,0:15:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakoku Sovereignty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.78,0:15:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.56,0:15:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oimo and Kashii went out to pick up\NDorry and Brogy as they said.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But they got caught and fooled\Nby the Navy on their way{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and were forced to guard the gate at Enies Lobby\Nfor half a century.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then, it was none other than Sniper King\Nwho taught them the truth and freed them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.25,0:15:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After learning the truth,\NKashii and Oimo became allies of Luffy and the others{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and created havoc in Enies Lobby.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.09,0:16:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Linlin! Did you guys finish preparing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.81,0:16:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kashii, preparing for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.98,0:16:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Linlin-{\i1}chan{\i0}, I guess \Nit's your first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.48,0:16:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In Elbaph, we undergo fasting for 12 days\Nbefore the Winter Solstice Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.67,0:16:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fasting?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.43,0:16:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't eat anything.\NYou're only allowed to drink water.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.78,0:16:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For 12 days starting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.93,0:16:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.33,0:16:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.23,0:16:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you can endure it,\Nwe'll have a festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.17,0:16:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight against yourself, Hajrudin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.93,0:16:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up, Hajrudin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:52.58,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This Giant boy, Hajrudin...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:55.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,HAJRUDIN
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.99,0:17:02.23,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...will eventually meet Luffy in Dressrosa\Nand be impressed by his determination.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:04.08,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Along with Bartolomeo and the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:07.24,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,he exchanged cups of {\i0}sake{\i1} as \Nparent and son with Luffy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.26,0:17:13.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He is now a member of the Straw Hat Fleet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.08,0:17:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tough boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.52,0:17:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dorry or Brogy, either \Nof the chiefs will return
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.23,0:17:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Giant Pirates \Nwill roam again for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.44,0:17:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a warrior!\NDon't stop training yourself, Hajrudin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.34,0:17:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.81,0:17:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like the spirit! Rydin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.10,0:17:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.78,0:17:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Beardfall-{\i1}sama{\i0}! Chief Beardhill-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.78,0:17:45.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,CHIEF BEARDHILL JARUL (345 YEARS OLD)\NCHIEF BEARDFALL JORUL (344 YEARS OLD)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.24,0:17:49.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Carmel preaches "trade rather than \Nrobbery" and that's good too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we shall not forget that we are warriors!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.98,0:17:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.06,0:17:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jarul-{\i1}sama{\i0} and Jorul-{\i1}sama {\i0}are so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.38,0:17:58.65,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,FORMER CO-CAPTAINS OF THE GIANT PIRATES\N(TWO OF THE WORLD'S OLDEST WARRIORS)\NHEROES OF THE GIANTS
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.67,0:18:02.25,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder all Giants \Nrespect them as warriors!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.27,0:18:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna be like them some day!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.57,0:18:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What brought both of you here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll eat Semla in the village so we came here\Nto pick up the children at the House of Lambs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.89,0:18:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just in time, Linlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.63,0:18:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's Semla?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a very delicious sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! A sweet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.89,0:18:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before the fast, we'll get a lot of nutrition\Nby eating Semla!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we gonna eat it now? The sweet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.49,0:18:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet cream dolloped in\Nsweet bread with marzipan,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,topped with a dusting of sugar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.73,0:18:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the fun before the fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.22,0:18:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.24,0:18:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The recent birth of Prince \NLoki at the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.37,0:19:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Rodo and Goldberg who \Nwere born in the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank the Sun for our children's growth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.31,0:19:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank the Sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.39,0:19:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Semla!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.31,0:19:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a lot so eat as much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... Semla...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.40,0:19:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Linlin, eat, eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.07,0:19:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.09,0:19:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S... S...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.76,0:19:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.97,0:19:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.57,0:19:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.56,0:19:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious! Delicious! Sweet! Sweet!\NDelicious! Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious! Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.49,0:19:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Delicious! Delicious!\N--Whoa-whoa! Hey, Linlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.97,0:19:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't eat so fast!\NThere won't be enough to go around!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.68,0:20:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget to thank the Sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Semla!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.92,0:20:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious! It's so delicious! Semla!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:18.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,FASTING - DAY 3
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.10,0:20:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother... I'm starved to death...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.71,0:20:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Winter Solstice Festival celebrates\Nthe death and the resurrection of the Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting through the severe winter,\Nthe Sun will shine down on us again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.20,0:20:34.35,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,FASTING - DAY 4
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.37,0:20:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more you suffer,\Nthe more you appreciate the Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.26,0:20:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... let's keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.71,0:20:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Mother says so, I'll... keep trying...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.47,0:20:55.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,FASTING - DAY 5
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.89,0:20:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm losing weight...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.54,0:20:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.08,0:21:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.75,0:21:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Linlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing great! A little more to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.11,0:21:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.13,0:21:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Linlin started liking Mother so much.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.66,0:21:17.81,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,FASTING - DAY 6
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.83,0:21:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Semla was so delicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.87,0:21:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.54,0:21:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...wanna eat it... again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:39.35,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,FASTING - DAY 7
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.37,0:21:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.44,0:21:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, help!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.86,0:21:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Gerd?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.53,0:21:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Linlin-{\i1}chan{\i0} is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.16,0:22:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.45,0:22:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Semla!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.79,0:22:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.59,0:22:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Linlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.15,0:22:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me Semla...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.78,0:22:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Semla!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.43,0:22:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Linlin destroyed the village of Elbaph!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.27,0:22:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a nightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.61,0:22:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She finally did it! Linlin!\NShe has no right to thank the Sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.79,0:22:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she's a child,\Nwe can't forgive everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.14,0:22:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jorul-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.82,0:22:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Semla... Semla...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.74,0:22:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carmel... I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.05,0:22:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She may look like a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.20,0:22:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it! Jorul-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.81,0:22:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's a god of Disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:23:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Semla...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.65,0:23:16.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A huge event occurs that will change the fate of\Nthe innocent monster Charlotte Linlin!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.17,0:23:18.84,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her long standing feud with the Giants and a
